---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About WorkFlowAI - Our Mission" description="Learn about WorkFlowAI's mission to empower professionals with practical AI automation blueprints.">
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden pt-12 pb-24">
    <!-- Glowing background effects -->
    <div class="glow-orb glow-orb-indigo" style="top:-10%;left:-10%"></div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <!-- Title -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 rounded-full text-indigo-300 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">
          ✨ Our Philosophy
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight">
          Empowering the <span class="text-gradient">Automators</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We believe AI shouldn't just be talked about; it should be integrated. WorkFlowAI is a community-driven repository of free, copy-paste automation blueprints.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-300">
        <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/6">
          <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Founded with a simple observation: the internet is saturated with generic "AI directory lists" that offer zero value. Operations managers, solo founders, and marketers know that AI is powerful, but they get stuck trying to connect the APIs and webhooks.
          </p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            We built WorkFlowAI to bridge this gap. We don't just list tools; we publish actual blueprints. We map out data flows, write production-ready system prompts, and package them as free, downloadable files.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Our Values</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/6">
              <span class="text-3xl block mb-3">🛠️</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Immediate Utility</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">No generic listicles. Every page includes copy-paste assets and download links.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/6">
              <span class="text-3xl block mb-3">🔒</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Unbiased & Free</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">All blueprints are open-source and free to import without paywalls or subscriptions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/6">
              <span class="text-3xl block mb-3">👥</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Community Driven</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Workflows are built in public based on real Reddit and community automation requests.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/6 text-center italic text-indigo-300">
          "The future belongs to the operators who know how to connect APIs and instruct models."
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
